      "title": "Parallelism Abstractions in Eden",
      "abstract": "Two important abstractions have contributed to create a reliable programming methodology for industrial-strength programs These are functional abstraction (which has received different names in programming languages, such as procedure, subroutine, function, etc), and data abstraction (also with different names such as abstract data type, object, package or simply module). In both abstractions two different pieces of information are distinguished:"
